comment: Alt. route. Tracked with watch. Had to pause at red light.
Changed route to avoid detours and finish mile before last uphill section.
Unexpected detours because of closed sidewalks.
Strong headwind but I could reduce parachute effect somewhat by opening mesh part of roof to let air blow through the roof.
Strong headwind with light snow. The stroller roof acted like a parachute. The block of under-construction gravel road finally got paved over.
Had to be back home for an appointment.
I think I got the idea to compete with myself here.
